parameters:
Clea: Excuse me, I'm from the Adventurer's Guild. This is a
bento from the cafeteria.

Shopkeeper: I'm sorry for the trouble, but I appreciate
your help.

Shopkeeper: After Celis-chan, another female member? I
wonder if Agonia-san has something in mind.

Shopkeeper: If you're a member of the guild, you should
remember this. The former guild master of the Adventurer's
Guild was a woman.

Shopkeeper: Even the great widow Agonia-san, Storge, and
Shimos couldn't match her.
Thief Nora: Was there someone named Shimos-san?

Shopkeeper: That one is quite different from the others...
Speaking of Shimos, would you mind delivering this to the
armor shop?
Clea: Understood, I will deliver it.

Shopkeeper: Aren't you the Dragon Slayers! Keep up the good
work for the Adventurer's Guild from now on!

events.name: 食堂の忘れ物並列処理
